celssc-mode.el --- mode for editing celestia's catalog files.

Celestia is a free space simulation programm (http://www.shatters.net/celestia/).

You can find it here: Lisp:celssc-mode.el

=== Installation ===

Put celssc-mode.el in your load-path and this in your .emacs file:
  
 (autoload 'celssc-mode "celssc-mode" "Major mode for editing celesita's solar system catalog files" t)
 (setq auto-mode-alist (cons '("\\.ssc" . celssc-mode)
                                   auto-mode-alist))
 (autoload 'celssc-mode "celssc-mode" "Major mode for editing celesita's star catalog files" t)
 (setq auto-mode-alist (cons '("\\.stc" . celssc-mode)
                                   auto-mode-alist))
 (autoload 'celssc-mode "celssc-mode" "Major mode for editing celesita's deep sky objects files" t)
 (setq auto-mode-alist (cons '("\\.dsc" . celssc-mode)
                                   auto-mode-alist))
